rary with the Orange brand colors for example.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","title":"Theme Orange","role":"collection","kind":"symbol"}}}